16
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,560
Listen.

17
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,239
Kuding tea is good for you.

18
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:08,919
Alright, listen to Qiang.

19
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:18,199
- Ming.
- Boss.

20
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:19,280
Make Kuding tea for Mr. Ming.

21
00:02:20,479 --> 00:02:21,719
Okay, sure. In a moment.

22
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,319
Miss. How many of you?

23
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,479
Just one, any seat available?

24
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:30,639
Just a moment.

25
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,800
Here, take this number first.

26
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,680
Do I need to wait long?

27
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:42,120
I think it will take some time.

28
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,759
Are you in a hurry?

29
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:44,919
Not at all, I can wait.

30
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:45,920
I can wait.

31
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:49,960
- Take a look what you want like to order.
- Okay.

32
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,319
- Alright. Thank you.
- Okay.

33
00:02:54,784 --> 00:02:58,048
<i>[Episode Four]</i>

34
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:02,176
<i>Miss Mai, your flight ticket
for tomorrow morning is booked. See you then.</i>

35
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,560
- Miss.
<i>- Okay, see you tomorrow.</i>

36
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,568
Miss.

37
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,719
What would you like to eat?

38
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,719
Well, spiced salt mantis shrimp.

39
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:17,639
Not available, choose something else.

40
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,680
Isn't it a signature dish?

41
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,439
The stock today is not good.

42
